======
 AWAY 
======
| 

about
-----
| 

:author:  Bart Thate <bthate@gmail.com>
:contact: IRCNET/#dunkbots
:distribution: core
:license: Public Domain
 
| 

description
-----------
| 

keep notice of who's away

| 

  keep away messages 

| 

commands
--------
| 

1) *away-disable*

    :description: disable the away plugin

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !away-disable
        <output> away disabled


2) *away-enable*

    :description: enable the away plugin

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !away-enable
        <output> away enabled


